* Gardhere : [[Gaaljecel]], [[Garre]], [[Degoodi|Degodi]] iyo Awrmale<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=XpdAzRYruCwC|title=The Invention of Somalia|last=Ahmed|first=Ali Jimale|date=1995-01-01|publisher=The Red Sea Press|year=|isbn=9780932415998|location=|pages=122|language=en|via=}}</ref>
* Mayle: [[Xawaadle]]
* Maqarre: Ajuuraan , Dabarre and Irrole<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=XpdAzRYruCwC|title=The Invention of Somalia|last=Ahmed|first=Ali Jimale|date=1995-01-01|publisher=The Red Sea Press|year=|isbn=9780932415998|location=|pages=130|language=en|via=}}</ref>
